name: IF AND ELSEIF
formula:
IF 
[R_NAME]='EUROPE' AND [N_NAME] ='UK' THEN 'UK' ELSEIF
[R_NAME]='EUROPE' AND [N_NAME] ='FRANCE' THEN 'FRANCE' ELSE 'UNKNOWN' END

name: NESTEDIF
formula:
IF 
[R_NAME]='EUROPE' AND [N_NAME] ='UK' THEN 

(
IF 
[R_NAME]='EUROPE' THEN [R_NAME]+'-'+[N_NAME] ELSE [R_NAME] END
)

ELSEIF

[R_NAME]='EUROPE' AND [N_NAME] ='FRANCE' THEN 'FRANCE' ELSE 'UNKNOWN' END
